暂时用粗暴的方式进行修改以解决该问题:
修改点1: org.apache.dubbo.rpc.RpcContext#startAsync
如果当前线程是dubbo线程的话，打一个标识，并把当前线程的名称设置到value，为后续使用。因为只有dubbo线程和其他线程共享数据时才会有该问题，所以需要增加一个dubbo线程的标识。
```
  public static AsyncContext startAsync() throws IllegalStateException {
        RpcContext currentContext = getContext();
        if (currentContext.asyncContext == null) {
            currentContext.asyncContext = new AsyncContextImpl();
        }
        currentContext.asyncContext.start();
        appendDubboThreadInfo();
        return currentContext.asyncContext;
    }

    private static void appendDubboThreadInfo() {
        if (Thread.currentThread().getName().startsWith(AbstractServer.SERVER_THREAD_POOL_NAME)) {
            RpcContext.getContext().setAttachment(DUBBO_THREAD_SIGN, Thread.currentThread().getName());
        }
    }
```
改动点2: org.apache.dubbo.rpc.AsyncContextImpl#signalContextSwitch
在共享RpcContext时，需要判断当前线程的attachments中有无dubbo标识，没有dubbo标识的话，说明这个共享没有在dubbo线程与其他线程之前，不管。并且判断当前AsyncContextImpl的storeContext和当前线程的RpcContext是否一致，有可能在同一个线程中调用signalContextSwitch();这种情况需要排除。满足要求后，设置SHARE_CONTEXT_SIGN值，为后续ConsumerContextFilter的clearAttachments判断用。
```
 public void signalContextSwitch() {
        //add the share context sign
        if (storedContext.getAttachments().containsKey(DUBBO_THREAD_SIGN) && RpcContext.getContext() != storedContext) {
            storedContext.setAttachment(SHARE_CONTEXT_SIGN, String.valueOf(Boolean.TRUE));
        }
        RpcContext.restoreContext(storedContext);
        RpcContext.restoreServerContext(storedServerContext);
        // Restore any other contexts in here if necessary.
    }
```


改动点3: org.apache.dubbo.rpc.filter.ConsumerContextFilter#invoke
在clear attachments之后，需要判断一下SHARE_CONTEXT_SIGN有没有被Dubbo线程删除，因为clear必须要在Dubbo线程的RpcContext copyOf操作之后。所以这里重试3次，如果dubbo线程一直没有copyOf完成，这里就抛出异常，证明dubbo线程执行太慢了，本次调用失败。
 ```
public Result invoke(Invoker<?> invoker, Invocation invocation) throws RpcException {
        RpcContext.getContext()
                .setInvoker(invoker)
                .setInvocation(invocation)
                .setLocalAddress(NetUtils.getLocalHost(), 0)
                .setRemoteAddress(invoker.getUrl().getHost(),
                        invoker.getUrl().getPort());
        if (invocation instanceof RpcInvocation) {
            ((RpcInvocation) invocation).setInvoker(invoker);
        }
        try {
            // TODO should we clear server context?
            RpcContext.removeServerContext();
            return invoker.invoke(invocation);
        } finally {
            // TODO removeContext? but we need to save future for RpcContext.getFuture() API. If clear attachments here, attachments will not available when postProcessResult is invoked.
            //check attachments share context sign
            checkShareContextSign();
            RpcContext.getContext().clearAttachments();
        }
    }

     private void checkShareContextSign() {
        int retryCount = 3;
        long retry_internal = RpcContext.getContext().getAttachments().size() < 1000 ? 10 : 20;
        for (int i = 0; i < retryCount; i++) {
            boolean isShareContext = RpcContext.getContext().getAttachments().containsKey(SHARE_CONTEXT_SIGN);
            if (!isShareContext) {
                return;
            }
            try {
                Thread.sleep(retry_internal);
            } catch (InterruptedException e) {
                e.printStackTrace();
            }
        }
        throw new RpcException("Concurrent Exception, the biz Thread is faster than dubbo thread");
    }
```



改动点4: org.apache.dubbo.rpc.AsyncRpcResult#AsyncRpcResult(java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<java.lang.Object>, java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture<org.apache.dubbo.rpc.Result>, boolean)
在AsyncRpcResult的RpcContext copyOf操作过后，需要清除SHARE_CONTEXT_SIGN值，这里需要判断，只有当前线程和之前设置dubbo线程的值一致时，才进行删除。因为其他线程也可能会走到这里来。

```
 public AsyncRpcResult(CompletableFuture<Object> future, final CompletableFuture<Result> rFuture, boolean registerCallback) {
        if (rFuture == null) {
            throw new IllegalArgumentException();
        }
        resultFuture = rFuture;
        if (registerCallback) {
            /**
             * We do not know whether future already completed or not, it's a future exposed or even created by end user.
             * 1. future complete before whenComplete. whenComplete fn (resultFuture.complete) will be executed in thread subscribing, in our case, it's Dubbo thread.
             * 2. future complete after whenComplete. whenComplete fn (resultFuture.complete) will be executed in thread calling complete, normally its User thread.
             */
            future.whenComplete((v, t) -> {
                RpcResult rpcResult;
                if (t != null) {
                    if (t instanceof CompletionException) {
                        rpcResult = new RpcResult(t.getCause());
                    } else {
                        rpcResult = new RpcResult(t);
                    }
                } else {
                    rpcResult = new RpcResult(v);
                }
                // instead of resultFuture we must use rFuture here, resultFuture may being changed before complete when building filter chain, but rFuture was guaranteed never changed by closure.
                rFuture.complete(rpcResult);
            });
        }
        this.valueFuture = future;
        // employ copy of context avoid the other call may modify the context content
        this.storedContext = RpcContext.getContext().copyOf();
        this.storedServerContext = RpcContext.getServerContext().copyOf();
        removeShareContextInfo();
    }

    private void removeShareContextInfo() {
        Map<String, String> attachments = RpcContext.getContext().getAttachments();
        if (attachments.containsKey(DUBBO_THREAD_SIGN) && attachments.containsKey(SHARE_CONTEXT_SIGN)) {
            if (attachments.get(DUBBO_THREAD_SIGN).equals(Thread.currentThread().getName())) {
                attachments.remove(DUBBO_THREAD_SIGN);
                attachments.remove(SHARE_CONTEXT_SIGN);
            }
        }
    }
```

